README 
Makefile  

********************************************************************************
** Computation of the Gegenbauer coefficients by using the first
** algorithm making use of FFT of the Abel-type transform of the
** input function.

ggb_coeff_fft.c 	Contains the main routine
call_ggb_coeff_fft.c   	Interface calling the main routine for testing

********************************************************************************
** Computation of the Gegenbauer coefficients by the using the 
** second algorithm making use of Gauss-Jacobi quadrature.

ggb_coeff_jacobi.cpp   contains the main routine
call_ggb_coeff_jacobi.cpp interface calling the main routine for testing

********************************************************************************
** Computation of the \sum f(cos u) (or f(x)) of a Gegenbauer expansion from 
** the Gegenbauer coefficients by computing the Abel-type integral of a 
** suitable (inverse) FFT of the Gegenbauer coefficients. 

ggb_inversion_no_fft.c        Computation of the sum of the Gegenbauer expansion
call_ggb_inversion_fft.c      Interface for testing 

********************************************************************************
** Computation of the \sum f(cos u) (or f(x)) of a Gegenbauer expansion from 
** the Gegenbauer coefficients by computing the Abel-type integral of a 
** suitable (inverse) cosine-transform of the Gegenbauer coefficients, 
** implemented without using the FFT.

call_ggb_inversion_no_fft.c Interface for testing
ggb_inversion_fft.c	    Computation of the sum of the Gegenbauer expansion

********************************************************************************
** This file contains the function whose Gegenbauer coefficients are computed

function.c   

